{"tid":1837893,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"天時地利人和，支爆嘅鐘聲響起了","createTime":"2020-01-23T22:04:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T22:18:01.000Z","uid":91659,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"41fa1d4570569c40814e802cc0de6f5171424a19","tid":1837893,"uid":91659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T22:04:05.000Z","msg":"啟示錄中記載嘅末世四騎士 (the 4 harbinger horsemen)，已經逐漸來到中国<br />\n<br />\n先有同豬瘟伴隨而黎嘅 Famine 饑荒<br />\n<br />\n緊隨其後嘅 Pestilence 瘟疫，武漢肺炎呢隻黑天鵝，习大大年頭話要防，不過都係眼白白睇住佢降臨<br />\n<br />\n而家 Death 死亡都參一腳，向中共人民宣揚末世到來<br />\n<br />\n好快最後一位騎士 War 戰爭就會全面進場。1911 年辛亥革命發源地喺邊度？就係武漢呀！<br />\n<br />\n當末世四騎士到齊之時，滅共鐘聲就會響起，到時全世界都會應聲討伐支共，建黨九十九年，終鑄成大錯！<br />\n<br />\n到時代表希望嘅新四騎士都會應驗而起：<br />\n解放人權嘅新疆，解放自由思想和宗教嘅西藏，解放民主民權嘅台灣，以及解放智慧與道德嘅香港！香港的子民啊，應兆奮起吧！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論：鬼叫你維尼走去重編聖經咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />耶和華份人對於不義之人好小氣架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"940453334597b11bc8338f04d0c3a51a6b3194a8","tid":1837893,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T22:06:35.000Z","msg":"光輝歲月？"},{"pid":"6374b1037d1975ad3c09e422b5a7cd09b70ca919","tid":1837893,"uid":218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T22:15:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.nieuwsblad.be/Assets/Images_Upload/2018/12/28/14cd93f4-0aa0-11e9-977e-abc59a2e673c_web_scale_0.1726747_0.1726747__.jpg?maxheight=513&amp;maxwidth=767&amp;scale=both\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.nieuwsblad.be%2FAssets%2FImages_Upload%2F2018%2F12%2F28%2F14cd93f4-0aa0-11e9-977e-abc59a2e673c_web_scale_0.1726747_0.1726747__.jpg%3Fmaxheight%3D513%26maxwidth%3D767%26scale%3Dboth&h=6954ae0a&s={SIZE}\" /> VS<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201805/f9558f404fef4b5ae7e7406e3149c61e.PNG\" data-th